---
---

<!-- Purpose Section (Visi Misi without the labels) -->
<section class="py-20 bg-transparent relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Vision Area -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-5/12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-display text-content">Tujuan Besar Kami</h2>
          <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-primary/40 rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xl font-medium text-content leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Menjadi komunitas yang mendukung dan menghubungkan semua orang yang berbahagia dengan event yang menyediakan ruang untuk <span class="text-primary font-bold">berekspresi, berkreasi, dan berkolaborasi</span>, terutama dalam hal budaya Jepang dan pop culture lainnya.
        </p>
        <div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/40 border border-white/60 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-md relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 opacity-10 rotate-12">
            <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-primary" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-1-13h2v6h-2zm0 8h2v2h-2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-content font-medium font-body text-sm italic relative z-10">
            Membawa semangat kebersamaan untuk terus menghidupkan karya dan imajinasi melalui komunitas yang positif.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission Area -->
      <div class="w-full md:w-7/12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/40 rounded-2xl border border-white/60 p-6 hover:bg-white/50 hover:border-primary transition-all shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-display text-content mb-2">Eksplorasi Budaya</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-content/80 font-medium">Mengembangkan dan meningkatkan kesadaran akan budaya Jepang dan pop culture.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/40 rounded-2xl border border-white/60 p-6 hover:bg-white/50 hover:border-primary transition-all shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-display text-content mb-2">Ruang Inklusif</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-content/80 font-medium">Membangun komunitas yang inklusif dan selalu memberikan dukungan nyata satu sama lain.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/40 rounded-2xl border border-white/60 p-6 hover:bg-white/50 hover:border-primary transition-all shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-display text-content mb-2">Kreatif & Edukatif</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-content/80 font-medium">Mengadakan berbagai event dan kegiatan menarik yang kreatif serta memiliki nilai edukasi.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/40 rounded-2xl border border-white/60 p-6 hover:bg-white/50 hover:border-primary transition-all shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:-translate-y-1">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-display text-content mb-2">Kolaborasi & Potensi</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-content/80 font-medium">Mengembangkan jaringan kolaborasi dengan komunitas lain dan meningkatkan kapasitas anggota komunitas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
